WEBVTT

00:02.096 --> 00:05.264
The world as they knew it has been destroyed by Typhoon Haiyan.

00:05.471 --> 00:09.330
And now, the children of the Philippines need our help to survive.

00:09.592 --> 00:15.027
UNICEF has helped save more children's lives than any humanitarian organization in the world.

00:15.428 --> 00:21.596
UNICEF delivers life-saving clean water, nutrition, immunization and health care in emergencies,...

00:21.733 --> 00:23.349
...but we need your help.

00:24.038 --> 00:31.604
Text "GIVE" to 45678 to donate ten dollars or visit unicef.ca.

